Row 1:& & & & & & & & 1 & & 1\\\noalign{\smallskip\smallskip}
Row 2:& & & & & & & 1 & & 2 & & 1\\\noalign{\smallskip\smallskip}
Row 3:& & & & & & 1 & & 3 & & 3 & & 1\\\noalign{\smallskip\smallskip}
Row 4:& & & & & 1 & & 4 & & 6 & & 4 & & 1\\\noalign{\smallskip\smallskip}
